data.description: If you are looking for a great house to start your family in, or downsize look no further. This beautiful 3 bedroom 2 bath home, in the desired New Forest neighborhood, has a nice shaded backyard with room for your family to relax or play. On those cold days come in to the spacious living room and get warmed by the fire and watch your family's favorite movie or read a book. The neighborhood is great and has a nice pool, playground and splash pad for the kids or grandkids when they come to visit. Roof has been recently replaced! Schedule your showing today!!!
